data.description:
Huge corner lot home for sale in the marina district of Gulfport, Florida. Just one block from a full service marina where kayaks and paddle boards allow you to discover Clam Bayou and Boca Ciega Bay. 
Beautiful walking/running trails along the bay and a great place to bring your dog.

-Hot water heater 2020
-New updated electrical 2020
-New ac 2020
This 2 bedroom, 1 bath corner lot home features a TWO-CAR OVER-SIZED GARAGE so bring your boat or jetsk

Located under a mile from
downtown Gulfport, 15 minutes to the beach and downtown St. Petersburg. Close access to the interstate.

Gulfports fun and eclectic downtown includes restaurants, shops and is home to many events such as the Tuesday fresh market, First Friday and Second Saturday art walk and other activities.

Gulfport also has its own beach where you can catch a sunset yoga class or meditation. The Gulfport casino has events and dance classes and steps away are the volleyball courts.

This home is located conveniently near downtown, so you can easily grab your bike, your golf cart or walk to enjoy all that the unique town of Gulfport has to offer!
